  "detailed_description": "Welcome to MA3! In this open world game, you play the role of Mahi. Who lives in a busy city where crime happens frequently. you’ll live as a transporter but you also have a hidden life as a masked vigilante, MA3. MA3 saves people from the bad people such as kidnappers and killers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>As Mahi you’ll do some work like transporting cars and passengers.<br></li><li>As a side job you can drive a taxi.<br></li><li>You gain money from your work and can spend your earned money to buy food, guns, medicines and other items.<br></li><li>As the masked vigilante MA3 you save people from others and kill enemies such as kidnappers and killers.<br></li><li>When the public is disturbed the police will be on high alert and will targeted.<br></li><li>Expect a lot of mixed actions of physical combat, intense gun fights, sword fights, hunting animals and many more high octane moments.<br></li><li>Enjoy tearing up the streets in different cars and even steal police cars, but careful as you will be targeted by the police when you steal the police cars. </li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to MA3! In this open world game, you play the role of Mahi. Who lives in a busy city where crime happens frequently. you’ll live as a transporter but you also have a hidden life as a masked vigilante, MA3. MA3 saves people from the bad people such as kidnappers and killers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>As Mahi you’ll do some work like transporting cars and passengers.<br></li><li>As a side job you can drive a taxi.<br></li><li>You gain money from your work and can spend your earned money to buy food, guns, medicines and other items.<br></li><li>As the masked vigilante MA3 you save people from others and kill enemies such as kidnappers and killers.<br></li><li>When the public is disturbed the police will be on high alert and will targeted.<br></li><li>Expect a lot of mixed actions of physical combat, intense gun fights, sword fights, hunting animals and many more high octane moments.<br></li><li>Enjoy tearing up the streets in different cars and even steal police cars, but careful as you will be targeted by the police when you steal the police cars. </li></ul>",
